  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dc5\u0dcf\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9c\u0dab\u0db1\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dc3\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Rains in many provinces",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Department of Meteorology says that rain will occur from time to time in Western, Sabaragamuwa and North-Western provinces, Kandy, Nuwara Eliya, Galle and Matara districts today (28).",
        "A spokesperson of the department said that there will be scattered showers or thunderstorms in Uva, Eastern and Northern provinces in the evening or at night.",
        "Lightning and temporary gusty winds are also possible, the spokesman said."
      ],
